OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud soon breaking up to
OL,6,Fgive bright or sunny spells, but also
OL,7,Fscattered showers. The showers turning
OL,8,Fheavy, with the risk of hail and
OL,9,Fthunder in places, especially during
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Light winds generally,
OL,11,Fbut locally gusty near showers.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe heaviest of the showers
OL,14,Fgradually easing this evening.
OL,15,FBecoming largely dry with variable
OL,16,Fcloud and clear spells developing for
OL,17,Fmany. Light winds. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
